# Prerequisites

1. See [dough](pizza_dough.mwdn)
2. See [sauce](pizza_sauce.mdwn)

# Ingredients

* XXX pesto genovese
* XXX buffalo mozzarella
* 1-2 bell peppers

## Optional

* Fresh basil
* Oregano

# Preparation

1. Pre-heat oven to maximum. 300C and above are best. # TODO convection yes/no?
2. Slice buffalo mozzarella
3. Slice bell peppers
4. Roll out dough
5. Slather with sauce
6. Place mozzarella
7. Place bell peppers
8. Dribble pesto genovese
9. Put into oven, wait for 5-15m, depending on heat; you will need to figure this out depending on your oven. Write it down.
